          "number": 3,
          "type": "true_false",
          "content": "<p>$(2x - 3)^2 = 4x^2 - 12x + 9$。</p>",
          "answer": "○",
          "explanation": "<p>正確。$(2x)^2 - 2 \\times 2x \\times 3 + 3^2 = 4x^2 - 12x + 9$。</p>"
        },
