          "content": "<p>$\\left(\\frac{2}{3}\\right)^2 = \\frac{4}{6}$。</p>",
          "answer": "╳",
          "explanation": "<p>錯誤。分子分母都要平方，$\\left(\\frac{2}{3}\\right)^2 = \\frac{4}{9}$。</p>"
        },
