          "content": "<p>展開 $(x + 4)^2$。</p><p>A. $x^2 + 16$</p><p>B. $x^2 + 4x + 16$</p><p>C. $x^2 + 8x + 16$</p><p>D. $x^2 + 8x + 8$</p>",
