          "content": "<p>已知 $a + b = 7$、$ab = 10$，求 $(a-b)^2$。</p><p>A. 9</p><p>B. 19</p><p>C. 29</p><p>D. 49</p>",
          "answer": "A",
          "explanation": "<p>$(a-b)^2 = (a+b)^2 - 4ab = 49 - 40 = 9$（A）</p>"
