          "number": 13,
          "type": "single_choice",
          "content": "<p>已知 $a + \\frac{1}{a} = 4$，求 $a^2 + \\frac{1}{a^2}$。</p><p>A. 12</p><p>B. 14</p><p>C. 16</p><p>D. 18</p>",
          "answer": "B",
