          "content": "<p>計算 $(2-1)(2+1)(2^2+1)(2^4+1)(2^8+1)$。</p><p>A. $2^8 - 1$</p><p>B. $2^{15} - 1$</p><p>C. $2^{16} - 1$</p><p>D. $2^{16} + 1$</p>",
          "answer": "C",
