        {
          "id": "g2a_ch1_1_q15",
          "number": 15,
          "type": "multi_choice",
          "content": "<p>下列展開何者正確？（多選）</p><p>A. $(x+5)^2 = x^2 + 10x + 25$</p><p>B. $(x-3)^2 = x^2 - 6x - 9$</p><p>C. $(x+6)(x-6) = x^2 - 36$</p><p>D. $(2x+1)^2 = 4x^2 + 2x + 1$</p><p>E. $(a-b)^2 = (b-a)^2$</p>",
          "answer": "ACE",
          "explanation": "<p><strong>A ○</strong>：和平方正確。</p><p><strong>B ╳</strong>：應為 $x^2 - 6x + 9$，常數項要 $+9$。</p><p><strong>C ○</strong>：平方差正確。</p><p><strong>D ╳</strong>：中間項應為 $2 \\times 2x \\times 1 = 4x$，故為 $4x^2 + 4x + 1$。</p><p><strong>E ○</strong>：$(a-b)^2 = (b-a)^2$，因為平方後正負消失。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": "g2a_ch1_1_q16",
          "number": 16,
          "type": "multi_choice",
          "content": "<p>已知 $a + b = 6$、$ab = 5$，下列何者正確？（多選）</p><p>A. $a^2 + b^2 = 26$</p><p>B. $(a-b)^2 = 16$</p><p>C. $a - b = \\pm 4$</p><p>D. $a^2 - b^2 = 24$</p><p>E. $a^3 + b^3$ 可直接由 $a+b$ 與 $ab$ 求出</p>",
          "answer": "ABCE",
          "explanation": "<p><strong>A ○</strong>：$(a+b)^2 - 2ab = 36 - 10 = 26$。</p><p><strong>B ○</strong>：$(a+b)^2 - 4ab = 36 - 20 = 16$。</p><p><strong>C ○</strong>：$a - b = \\pm\\sqrt{16} = \\pm 4$（不可漏負）。</p><p><strong>D ╳</strong>：$a^2 - b^2 = (a+b)(a-b) = 6 \\times (\\pm 4) = \\pm 24$，不只 24。</p><p><strong>E ○</strong>：對稱式皆可由基本對稱式表示。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": "g2a_ch1_1_q17",
          "number": 17,
          "type": "multi_choice",
          "content": "<p>下列速算何者正確？（多選）</p><p>A. $101^2 = 10201$</p><p>B. $98 \\times 102 = 9996$</p><p>C. $999^2 = 998001$</p><p>D. $(100-1)(100+1) = 9999$</p><p>E. $50.5 \\times 49.5 = 2499.75$</p>",
          "answer": "ABCDE",
          "explanation": "<p><strong>A ○</strong>：$(100+1)^2 = 10000 + 200 + 1 = 10201$。</p><p><strong>B ○</strong>：$(100-2)(100+2) = 10000 - 4 = 9996$。</p><p><strong>C ○</strong>：$(1000-1)^2 = 1000000 - 2000 + 1 = 998001$。</p><p><strong>D ○</strong>：$100^2 - 1 = 9999$。</p><p><strong>E ○</strong>：$(50 + 0.5)(50 - 0.5) = 2500 - 0.25 = 2499.75$。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": "g2a_ch1_1_q18",
          "number": 18,
          "type": "multi_choice",
          "content": "<p>已知 $a - \\frac{1}{a} = 3$，下列何者正確？（多選）</p><p>A. $a^2 + \\frac{1}{a^2} = 11$</p><p>B. $\\left(a + \\frac{1}{a}\\right)^2 = 13$</p><p>C. $a + \\frac{1}{a} = \\pm\\sqrt{13}$</p><p>D. $a^2 - \\frac{1}{a^2} = 3\\left(a + \\frac{1}{a}\\right)$</p><p>E. $a^2 + \\frac{1}{a^2} = 9$</p>",
          "answer": "ABCD",
          "explanation": "<p><strong>A ○</strong>：$a^2 + \\frac{1}{a^2} = \\left(a - \\frac{1}{a}\\right)^2 + 2 = 9 + 2 = 11$。</p><p><strong>B ○</strong>：$\\left(a+\\frac{1}{a}\\right)^2 = a^2 + 2 + \\frac{1}{a^2} = 11 + 2 = 13$。</p><p><strong>C ○</strong>：開根號取正負。</p><p><strong>D ○</strong>：$a^2 - \\frac{1}{a^2} = \\left(a-\\frac{1}{a}\\right)\\left(a+\\frac{1}{a}\\right) = 3\\left(a+\\frac{1}{a}\\right)$。</p><p><strong>E ╳</strong>：應為 11 不是 9（漏加 $+2$）。</p>"
