          "number": 19,
          "type": "multi_choice",
          "content": "<p>關於 $(a+b+c)^2$ 的展開，下列何者正確？（多選）</p><p>A. 展開後共有 6 項</p><p>B. $(a+b+c)^2 = a^2 + b^2 + c^2 + 2ab + 2bc + 2ac$</p><p>C. 若 $a+b+c = 10$、$ab+bc+ac = 20$，則 $a^2+b^2+c^2 = 60$</p><p>D. $(1+2+3)^2 = 1 + 4 + 9 = 14$</p><p>E. $(x-y+z)^2 = x^2 + y^2 + z^2 - 2xy - 2yz + 2xz$</p>",
          "answer": "ABCE",
          "explanation": "<p><strong>A ○</strong>：3 個平方項 + 3 組兩兩乘積 = 6 項。</p><p><strong>B ○</strong>：三項和平方標準公式。</p><p><strong>C ○</strong>：$a^2+b^2+c^2 = (a+b+c)^2 - 2(ab+bc+ac) = 100 - 40 = 60$。</p><p><strong>D ╳</strong>：$(1+2+3)^2 = 6^2 = 36$，不是各項平方和。</p><p><strong>E ○</strong>：把 $-y$ 當 $b$ 代入：$-2x \\cdot y$、$-2y \\cdot z$、$+2x \\cdot z$，正確。</p>"
